xt <- xtabs(~ Occupation + Newspaper, data = news_reader)  #  
mosaicplot(xt, main = "Reader's occupation and newspaper", color = TRUE) #

    prog <- factor(prog)

  • \(\beta_0, \beta_1, ... \beta_k\) : (\(\beta_0\) : (intercept) , \(\beta_1, \beta_2, ... , \beta_k\) : (slope))

5.2.1 Multiple \(R{^2}\) Adjusted \(R{^2}\)

  • : SST = SSR + SSE
